    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Life on a desert island",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.27,
      "endTime": 9.6
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What was exceptional about the two men's stay on the desert island?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.61,
      "endTime": 16.23,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Most of us have formed an unrealistic picture of life on a desert island.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.24,
      "endTime": 22.18
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We sometimes imagine a desert island to be a sort of paradise where the sun always shines.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 22.19,
      "endTime": 29.84
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Life there is simple and good.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 29.85,
      "endTime": 32.43,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Ripe fruit falls from the trees and you never have to work.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 32.44,
      "endTime": 37.51,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The other side of the picture is quite the opposite.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 37.52,
      "endTime": 41.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Life on a desert island is wretched.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.16,
      "endTime": 43.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "You either starve to death or live like Robinson Crusoe, waiting for a boat which never comes.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 43.94,
      "endTime": 52.48,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Perhaps there is an element of truth in both these pictures, but few of us have had the opportunity to find out.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.49,
      "endTime": 60.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Two men who recently spent five days on a coral island wished they had stayed there longer.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 60.81,
      "endTime": 69.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Five",
            "pos": "num.",
            "meaning": "五"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They were taking a badly damaged boat from the Virgin Islands to Miami to have it repaired.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 69.25,
      "endTime": 75.84,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "During the journey, their boat began to sink.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 75.85,
      "endTime": 80.14,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They quickly loaded a small rubber dinghy with food, matches, and cans of beer and rowed for a few miles across the Caribbean until they arrived at a tiny coral island.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.15,
      "endTime": 93.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "There were hardly any trees on the island and there was no water, but this did not prove to be a problem.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 93.63,
      "endTime": 101.51,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The men collected rainwater in the rubber dinghy.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.52,
      "endTime": 105.27
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "As they had brought a spear gun with them, they had plenty to eat.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.28,
      "endTime": 109.55
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They caught lobster and fish every day, and as one of them put it 'ate like kings'.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 109.56,
      "endTime": 117.19,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When a passing tanker rescued them five days later, both men were genuinely sorry that they had to leave.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 117.2,
      "endTime": 122.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Five",
            "pos": "num.",
            "meaning": "五"
          },
          {
            "word": "Sorry",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "抱歉的"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
